%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BNo%20Priors%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20Thursday%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-ng-vibe-coding-unfortunate-term-exhausting-job-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-assisted%20coding%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20compressed%20the%20startup%20loop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20that%20used%20to%20take%20six%20engineers%20three%20months%20to%20build%2C%20%26quot%3Bmy%20friends%20and%20I%2C%20we'll%20just%20build%20on%20a%20weekend%2C%26quot%3B%20Ng%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bottleneck%20is%20deciding%20what%20do%20we%20actually%20want%20to%20build%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20a%20prototype%20might%20take%20three%20weeks%20to%20develop%2C%20so%20waiting%20another%20week%20for%20user%20feedback%20wasn't%20a%20big%20deal.%20But%20today%2C%20when%20a%20prototype%20can%20be%20built%20in%20a%20single%20day%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20have%20to%20wait%20a%20week%20for%20user%20feedback%2C%20that's%20really%20painful%2C%26quot%3B%20Ng%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20mismatch%20is%20forcing%20teams%20to%20make%20faster%20product%20decisions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Ng%20said%20his%20teams%20are%20%26quot%3Bincreasingly%20relying%20on%20gut.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20product%20managers%20bring%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20customer%20empathy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20It's%20not%20enough%20to%20crunch%20data%20on%20user%20behavior.%20They%20need%20to%20form%20a%20mental%20model%20of%20the%20ideal%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20ability%20to%20%26quot%3Bsynthesize%20lots%20of%20signals%20to%20really%20put%20yourself%20in%20the%20other%20person's%20shoes%20to%20then%20very%20rapidly%20make%20product%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENg%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ddc8a22d-aaac-41d7-9310-ddfb0ac3e3c4%5C%22%3EThe%20great%20product%20manager%20debate