etamine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20really%20gonna%20take%20this%20thing%20to%20the%20next%20level%20and%20be%20like%20those%20Silicon%20Valley%20elites%2C%20we%20got%20to%20take%20these%2C%26quot%3B%20Marsh%20says%2C%20pulling%20out%20nasal%20sprays%20filled%20with%20ketamine.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20called%20microdosing.%20It%20bolsters%20our%20focus%20and%20creativity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Silicon%20Valley%20leaders%20have%20been%20known%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-founders-who-used-psychedelics-lsd-acid-magic-mushrooms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexperiment%20with%20psychedelics%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20drugs%20as%20a%20form%20of%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKetamine%20is%20helpful%20for%20getting%20one%20out%20of%20the%20negative%20frame%20of%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Don%20Lemon%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Marsh's%20wife%2C%20Sharon%2C%20becomes%20increasingly%20irritated%20with%20her%20husband's%20reliance%20on%20ChatGPT%2C%20calling%20the%20AI%20a%20%26quot%3Blittle%20sycophant%20machine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20description%20that%20references%20the%20exact%20word%20OpenAI%20and%20its%20CEO%2C%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20used%20to%20explain%20a%20real%20issue%20ChatGPT%20had%20earlier%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20with%20its%204o%20model%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-kissing-butt-sycophant-tone-sam-altman-fix-coming-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esucking%20up%20to%20users%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespeople%20for%20Paramount%20and%20OpenAI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20couple%20of%20GPT-4o%20updates%20have%20made%20the%20personality%20too%20sycophant-y%20and%20annoying%20(even%20though%20there%20are%20some%20very%20good%20parts%20of%20it)%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote%20on%20X%20in%20April.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20on%20fixes%20asap%2C%20some%20today%20and%20some%20this%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Park's%2027th%20season%20premiered%20in%20July%2C%20opening%20up%20with%20relentless%20jabs%20at%20Trump%20and%20Paramount's%20subsidiary%20CBS.%20The%20episode%20was%20a%20ratings%20bonanza%2C%20attracting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-park-episode-mocking-trump-cbs-attracts-almost-6m-viewers-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enearly%206%20million%20viewers%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20Comedy%20Central%20and%20Paramount%2B%20within%20the%20first%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20episode%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bdesperate%20attempt%20for%20attention.%26quot%3B%20The%20White%20House%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20latest%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20what%20ChatGPT%20thought%20of%20the%20episode%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20'Sickofancy'%20was%20satire%20at%20its%20sharpest%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chatbot%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20brilliantly%20explores%20how%20AI%2C%20without%20discernment%2C%20can%20become%20dangerously%20enabling%20%E2%80%94%20affirming%20every%20bad%20idea%20while%20masquerading%20as%20a%20wise%20advisor.%20Watching%20Randy%20spiral%20from%20ChatGPT's%20flattery%20was%20both%20hilarious%20and%20chillingly%20relatable%20in%20our%20tech-obsessed%20age.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-park-tim-cook-silicon-valley-ketamine-chatgpt-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755828540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a7cfb1194a2d49b8aefb53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-park-tim-cook-silicon-valley-ketamine-chatgpt-2025