tion%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGarron%20Chiu%2C%20now%2037%2C%20was%20born%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20to%20Chinese%20parents%20and%20moved%20to%20Hong%20Kong%20as%20a%20kid.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20studied%20at%20an%20international%20high%20school%20and%20went%20back%20to%20the%20US%20for%20college.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%20back%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20his%20work%20in%20advertising%20and%20stand-up%20overlap%3A%20both%20demand%20insight%20into%20people%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Garron%20Chiu%2C%2037%2C%20an%20American-born%20Hongkonger%20who%20works%20in%20advertising%20and%20stand-up%20comedy.%20His%20words%20have%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20run%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-moo-moved-to-china-embrace-heritage-yayas-restaurateur-shanghai-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emy%20Asian%20identity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20a%20Westernized%20Chinese%20guy%20growing%20up%20between%20cultures%2C%20I%20thought%20the%20Asian%20part%20of%20me%20was%20less%20%26quot%3Bcool%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20Western%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20I%20run%20to%20it.%20I've%20learned%20that%20the%20contradiction%20of%20being%20Cantonese-speaking%2C%20Hong%20Kong-raised%2C%20and%20also%20very%20American%20is%20where%20the%20best%20comedy%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20born%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20to%20Chinese%20parents.%20In%20Pasadena%2C%20we%20were%20one%20of%20two%20Asian%20families%20on%20the%20block.%20When%20I%20was%204%2C%20my%20family%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flindsay-jang-entrepreneur-mom-finding-work-life-balance-hong-kong-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Hong%20Kong%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20I%20was%20in%20a%20city%20where%20everyone%20looked%20like%20me%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20cultural%20clash%20didn't%20go%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHong%20Kong%20is%20a%20remix%20city.%20The%20movies%2C%20the%20music%2C%20the%20food%3A%20Everything%20borrows%20from%20somewhere%20else%20and%20spins%20into%20something%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20my%20house%20was%20full%20of%20cultural%20crossovers.%20My%20parents%20loved%20traditional%20Cantonese%20pop%20music%20and%20'70s%20disco%20%E2%80%94%20ABBA%2C%20Earth%2C%20Wind%20%26amp%3B%20Fire%2C%20the%20Bee%20Gees.%20That%20mashup%20of%20influences%20shaped%20not%20just%20my%20sense%20of%20humor%2C%20but%20my%20entire%20worldview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282d36d2d-8902-482b-b898-1da53c990c69%5C%22%3ECollege%20in%20the%20US%20prepped%20me%20for%20stand-up%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20high%20school%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-hong-kong-moved-home-england-expat-networking-starting-over-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleft%20Hong%20Kong%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20US%20to%20study%20at%20Boston%20University%2C%20where%20I%20earned%20a%20Bachelor%20of%20Science%20degree.%20BU%20was%20a%20cultural%20collision%20in%20the%20best%20way%3A%20Some%20classmates%20had%20never%20left%20their%20home%20state%2C%20while%20others%20were%20more%20worldly%20than%20I%20was.%20Learning%20to%20connect%20across%20that%20spectrum%20prepared%20me%20for%20stand-up%20more%20than%20any%20textbook%20ever%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Garron%20Chiu%20at%20graduation%20from%20Boston%20University.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a59b8b194a2d49b8aed5c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChiu%20graduated%20from%20Boston%20University%20in%202010%20and%20moved%20back%20to%20Hong%20Kong.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Garron%20Chiu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EComedy%20is%20all%20about%20finding%20common%20grou