-real-tech-industry-right-2017-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESilicon%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20followed%20a%20crew%20of%20lame%2C%20socially%20awkward%20tech%20bros.%20The%20real%20Valley%20leaders%20weren't%20impressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkumail-nanjiani-habits-stay-fit-healthy-tour-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKumail%20Nanjiani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20actor%20from%20the%20hit%202010s%20HBO%20show%2C%20said%20that%20he%20met%20both%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg.%20On%20Mike%20Birbiglia's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY8zwAj3sYpc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWorking%20it%20Out%26quot%3B%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nanjiani%20described%20his%20interactions%20with%20the%20tech%20CEOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENanjiani%20said%20that%20Musk%20%26quot%3Bdidn't%20like%20the%20show%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20specifically%20its%20first%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20%26quot%3BSilicon%20Valley%2C%26quot%3B%20Kid%20Rock%20performs%20a%20rock%20set%20with%20electric%20guitars%20and%20strobe%20lights.%20After%20setting%20off%20sparklers%2C%20the%20camera%20cuts%20to%20the%20audience%2C%20revealing%20a%20scattered%20crowd%20of%20nerdy%20tech%20guys%20not%20paying%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElon%20was%20upset%2C%26quot%3B%20Nanjiani%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%20the%20parties%20I%20go%20to%20are%20much%20cooler%20than%20these%20parties.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20is%20known%20to%20party.%20In%202023%2C%20he%20attended%20a%20meeting%20with%20French%20President%20Emannuel%20Macron%20unshaven.%20Hours%20earlier%2C%20he%20was%20spotted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-unshaven-slept-car-clubbing-mexico-before-meeting-macron-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20dance%20floor%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20luxury%20resort%20in%20Cabo%20San%20Lucas%2C%20Mexico.