5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESalt%20%26amp%3B%20Stone%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E's%20deodorant%20isn't%20without%20a%20few%20caveats.%20At%20%2420%20for%202.6%20ounces%2C%20it's%20a%20splurge%20compared%20to%20drugstore%20options.%20Availability%20is%20also%20more%20in%20line%20with%20its%20premium%20positioning%3B%20you%20can%20find%20it%20at%20Sephora%2C%20Nordstrom%2C%20and%20Neiman%20Marcus%2C%20as%20well%20as%20online%20through%20the%20brand's%20website%2C%20those%20retailers%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20select%20specialty%20beauty%20shops.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20learned%20the%20hard%20way%20that%20it's%20essential%20to%20keep%20the%20product%20out%20of%20the%20sun.%20I%20had%20it%20sitting%20near%20a%20window%20in%20my%20closet%2C%20and%20after%20a%20few%20days%2C%20the%20balm%20started%20to%20separate%2C%20and%20I%20noticed%20an%20oil%20ring%20on%20my%20dresser%20where%20the%20deodorant%20was.%20Since%20then%2C%20I've%20kept%20it%20upright%20in%20a%20drawer%20and%20haven't%20seen%20the%20same%20issue%20since.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20if%20you're%20switching%20from%20an%20antiperspirant%20to%20%3Cem%3Eany%3C%2Fem%3E%20natural%20deodorant%2C%20you'll%20likely%20experience%20a%20short%20adjustment%20period%20with%20more%20sweat%20and%20odor.%20Your%20body%20may%20need%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20to%20detox%20from%20aluminum%20before%20your%20body%20fully%20normalizes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESalt%20%26amp%3B%20Stone%20is%20the%20rare%20natural%20deodorant%20that%20feels%20like%20a%20luxury%20fragrance%2C%20treats%20your%20skin%20like%20skincare%2C%20and%20keeps%20you%20fresh%20all%20day.%20It%20minimizes%20moisture%20without%20blocking%20sweat%20entirely%2C%20and%20doesn't%20wreck%20my%20clothing.%20Using%20it%20feels%20like%20a%20treat%2C%20not%20a%20compromise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIs%20it