ps%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650372f12a72d60019d56a19%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAttendees%20look%20out%20at%20the%20mud%20at%20Burning%20Man%202023.%3Cp%3EJULIE%20JAMMOT%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high-res%20Instagram%20pictures%20from%20Burning%20Man%20popping%20up%20on%20your%20Explore%20page%20likely%20come%20from%20attendees%20commonly%20known%20to%20Burners%20as%20%26quot%3BWeekend%20Warriors%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BSparkle%20Ponies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20people%20who%20come%20to%20the%20desert%20to%20snap%20pictures%20in%20six-inch%20platform%20boots%20and%20a%20%24600%20crystal-covered%20bodysuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20these%20people%20are%20the%201%25%2C%20but%20they%20also%20make%20up%201%25%20of%20Burning%20Man.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20much%20of%20Black%20Rock%20City%20%E2%80%94%20the%20temporary%20Nevada%20metropolis%20where%20Burning%20Man%20has%20been%20held%20every%20year%20since%201991%20%E2%80%94%20is%20built%20on%20the%20hard%20work%20and%20dedication%20of%20everyday%20people.%20In%20my%20camp%20alone%2C%20there%20were%20engineers%2C%20lawyers%2C%20hairdressers%2C%20and%20bartenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20camps%20have%20leadership%20teams%20that%20meet%20throughout%20the%20year%20to%20get%20ready%20for%20Burning%20Man.%20A%20lot%20of%20their%20effort%20is%20dedicated%20not%20to%20providing%20for%20people%20in%20the%20camp%2C%20but%20to%20creating%20a%20gift%20that%20will%20benefit%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20always%20been%20the%20core%20of%20what%20Burning%20Man%20is%20all%20about%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20mindset%20that%20I%20saw%20across%20the%20camps%20that%20fill%20the%20playa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMyth%20%232%3A%20You%20get%20everything%20at%20Burning%20Man%20by%20bartering.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22On%20top%20of%20Distrikt%20at%20Burning%20Man%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64fb52f23d3923001976fb42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20once%20among%20the%20many%20people%20who%20believed%20that%20Burning%20Man%20is%20built%20on%20a%20bartering%20system%20and%20that%20you%20have%20to%20bring%20items%20to%20Black%20Rock%20City%20to%20exchange%20and%20get%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20sure%20how%20this%20rumor%20started%2C%20but%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20that%20it%20is%20complete%20BS.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20goes%20against%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fburningman.org%2Fabout%2F10-principles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBurning%20Man's%2010%20guiding%20principles%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETruth%3A%20Burning%20Man%20is%20all%20about%20gifting.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Android%20Oasis%20Dome%20at%20Burning%20Man%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64fb73dda39a1b00190c26c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222656%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EChase%20Mitchell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBurning%20Man%20is%20devoted%20to%20acts%20of%20gift%20giving%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20reads%20in%20Burning%20Man's%20official%2010%20guiding%20principles.%20%26quot%3BThe%20value%20of%20a%20gift%20is%20unconditional.%20Gifting%20does%20not%20contemplate%20a%20return%20or%20an%20exchange%20for%20something%20of%20equal%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20find%20all%20kinds%20of%20gifts%20among%20the%20thousands%20of%20camps%20that%20fill%20the%20playa.%20And%20unlike%20the%20gifts%20you%20usually%20get%20for%20your%20birthday%20or%20the%20holidays%2C%20they%20won't%20be%20store-bought%20(decommodification%20is%20another%20of%20the%2010%20principles).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20camps%20offer%20manicures%20and%20foot%20massages%2C%20and%20others%20offer%20New%20York-style%20breakfast%20sandwiches.%20You'll%20find%20open%20bars%20on%20every%20corner%2C%20often%20accompanied%20by%20creative%20themes%20like%20being%20consensually%20abducted%20by%20%26quot%3Baliens%26quot%3B%20who%20capture%20you%20with%20a%20hula%20hoop%20and%20then%20shower%20you%20with%20compliments%20(this%20is%20a%20real%20camp%2C%20and%20it%20is%20awesome).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20camps%20throw%20parties%2C%20while%20others%20let%20you%20send%20postcards%20to%20your%20parents%20or%20dogs.%20My%20camp%2C%20Android%20Oasis%2C%20contributes%20a%20covered%20dome%20where%20anyone%20can%20stop%20by%20to%20cool%20down%20with%20ice-cold%20drinks%2C%20massages%2C%20and%20great%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurning%20Man%20is%20also%20founded%20on%20radical%20self-reliance%2C%20so%20you%20shouldn't%20just%20show%20up%20with%20nothing%20but%20hope%20in%20the%20generosity%20of%20others%20(although%20some%20people%20do).%20Most%20Burners%20don't%20come%20to%20Black%20Rock%20City%20wondering%20what%20they%20can%20get%20from%20people%20%E2%80%94%20but%20rather%20what%20they%20can%20give.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMyth%20%233%3A%20Burning%20Man%20is%20just%20one%20big%20music%20festival.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Burning%20Man%20festival%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663a9306b4abc992e8c6b605%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22723%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJULIE%20JAMMOT%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20celebrities%20and%20big-name%20DJs%20started%20popping%20up%20at%20Burning%20Man%2C%20it%20also%20began%20earning%20a%20reputation%20as%20an%20(even%20more)%20expensive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskipping-coachella-first-time-in-decade-not-the-same%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECoachella%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20frequently%20heard%20Burning%20Man%20referred%20to%20as%20a%20music%20festival%2C%20and%20many%20friends%20and%20coworkers%20have%20asked%20me%20if%20music%20is%20the%20main%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETruth%3A%20There's%20so%20much%20great%20music%20at%20Burning%20Man%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20the%20main%20event.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20100-person%20bike%20procession%20at%20Burning%20Man%20wedding%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650c6a6c12dc4f001a178c2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJulian%20Walter%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBurning%20Man%20attracts%20a%20ton%20of%20great%20DJs%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20many%20awesome%20sets%20during%20my%20week%20on%20the%20playa.%20At%20its%20core%2C%20however%2C%20Burning%20Man%20is%20a%20real%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20parties%20and%20shows%2C%20but%20you%20also%20work%20camp%20shifts%20and%20give%20back%20to%20the%20unique%20community.%20There%20are%20also%20dozens%20of%20sober%20camps%2C%20workshops%20that%20offer%20advice%20on%20everything%20from%20relationships%20to%20overcoming%20trauma%2C%20and%20Temple%2C%20where%20attendees%20go%20to%20reflect%20or%20process%20the%20loss%20of%20loved%20ones%20or%20recent%20difficult%20life%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlack%20Rock%20City%20has%20something%20for%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20the%20partiers%20or%20electronic%20music%20lovers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMyth%20%235%3A%20Burning%20Man%202023%20was%20%26quot%3BFyre%20Fest%202.0.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Muddy%20campground%20at%20Burning%20Man%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64fb52ee3d3923001976fb22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Ins