e%20most%20challenging%20environments%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rob%20Gamburg%2C%20the%20project%20lead%20for%20Silent%20Swarm%20at%20Naval%20Surface%20Warfare%20Center%2C%20Crane%20Division%20(NSWC%20Crane)%2C%20according%20to%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20didn't%20explicitly%20identify%20the%20drone%20present%20as%20fiber-optic%20drones%2C%20and%20the%20National%20Guard%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20clarity.%20But%20the%20spools%20are%20a%20giveaway.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETheir%20apparent%20involvement%20in%20the%20exercise%20is%20notable%20given%20their%20growing%20use%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20first%20introduced%20these%20drones%20as%20a%20way%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-fiber-optic-unjammable-drones-fix-a-big-problem-war-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebypass%20signal%20jamming%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20which%20became%20a%20prominent%20countermeasure%20for%20breaking%20the%20connection%20between%20the%20drone%20and%20operator%2C%20shutting%20down%20video%20feeds%2C%20and%20causing%20drones%20dependent%20on%20radio%20frequencies%20to%20malfunction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia%20have%20since%20ramped%20up%20their%20use%20of%20fiber-optic%20drones%2C%20leaving%20some%20battlefields%20littered%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funjammable-fiber-optic-drones-are-covering-ukrainian-forests-in-wires-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ediscarded%20cables%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Immune%20to%20jamming%2C%20these%20drones%20can%20deliver%20precise%20strikes%20at%20ranges%20of%20more%20than%2040%20kilometers%2C%20and%20manufacturers%20are%20already%20working%20to%20push%20that%20distance%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20small%2C%20black%20ground%20drones%20on%20wheels%20sit%20on%20the%20beach%20with%20a%20clear%20blue%2