0used%20coffee%20grounds%2C%20flour%2C%20and%20crushed%20cereal%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20much%20it%20sucked%20%E2%80%94%20pun%20intended.%20It%20vacuumed%20around%2085%25%20of%20spilled%20coffee%20grounds%2C%2082%25%20of%20spilled%20flour%2C%20and%2095%25%20of%20the%20crushed%20up%20Cheerios.%20The%20mid-range%20suction%20level%20is%20also%20a%20contributing%20factor%20for%20its%20inability%20to%20pull%20the%20smaller%20particles%20from%20crevices%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20models.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20I%20noticed%20while%20watching%20its%20various%20treks%20across%20different%20types%20of%20rugs%20was%20that%20its%20petite%20size%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20double-edged%20sword.%20I%20often%20saw%20it%20bounce%20across%20carpet%2C%20less%20firm%20and%20planted%20compared%20to%20hard%20floor%20surfaces.%20It%20was%20also%20noticeably%20loud%20on%20boost%20mode.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20area%20it%20performed%20only%20decently%20was%20its%20ability%20to%20get%20into%20corners.%20I%20spread%20a%20line%20of%20flour%20out%20from%20a%20corner%2C%20and%20the%20C20%20collected%20about%2075%25%20of%20the%20debris.%20This%20was%20a%20better%20performance%20than%20the%20iRobot%20Roomba%20205's%2060%25%2C%20but%20far%20from%20the%2097%25%20of%20the%20very%20expensive%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Froborock-saros-z70-preview-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERoborock%20Saros%20Z70%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20several%20weeks%20of%20use%2C%20I%20found%20only%20a%20few%20strands%20of%20hair%20on%20the%20main%20roller%2C%20though%20the%20side%20brush%20collected%20more.%20Unlike%20snap-off%20designs%2C%20the%20side%20brush%20also%20requires%20a%20Philips%20Head%20screwdriver%20for%20removal.%20Eufy%20recommends%20the%20C20%20for%20short-haired%20pets%2C%20and%20based%20on%20my%20tests%2C%20it%20should%20handle%20light%20fur%20but%20could%20get%20overwhelmed%20with%20heavier%20shedding.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22eufy%20omni%20c20%20cleans%20mustard%20stain%20on%20hardwood%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a6427fa17a8c5b4053332e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Eufy%20Omni%20C20%20was%20able%20to%20mop%20up%20mustard%20I%20spilled%20on%20the%20floor%20without%20much%20difficulty%2C%20but%20it%20did%20transfer%20a%20little%20residue%20on%20to%20my%20carpet%20when%20the%20mop%20lifting%20mechanism%20didn't%20go%20high%20enough.%20%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228af8fd40-63ee-4d48-8e52-41cb4bd2dc8e%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMopping%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20didn't%20find%20the%20C20%20to%20be%20a%20mopping%20powerhouse%20like%20the%20Shark%20PowerDetect%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20plenty%20effective.%20Its%20twin%20mop%20pads%20spin%20180%20times%20per%20minute%20with%206N%20of%20pressure%2C%20about%20average%20for%20this%20category.%20Using%20the%20mopping%20and%20vacuuming%20setting%2C%20it%20vacuumed%20and%20mopped%2095%25%20of%20the%20coffee%20grounds%2C%2089%25%20of%20the%20flour%2C%20and%2099%25%20of%20the%20crushed%20cereal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20weakest%20performance%20was%20with%20the%20flour%2C%20which%20made%20a%20slight%20mess%20and%20showed%20a%20light%20smear%20on%20its%20final%20pass.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20C20%20was%20able%20to%20handle%20drops%20of%20splattered%20mustard%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20but%20not%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Shark%20PowerDetect%2C%20and%20ended%20up%20leaving%20a%20few%20traces%20during%20a%20normal%20kitchen%20cleaning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22look%20at%20the%20underneath%20of%20the%20eufy%20omni%20c20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a6427fcfc04e97619bbddc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20twin%20microfiber%20mop%20pads%20are%20supposed%20to%20lift%20up%20when%20they%20detect%20carpet.%20I%20didn't%20notice%20much%20hair%20wrap%20around%20the%20brushroll%20or%20side%20brushes%2C%20either.%20%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20good%20news%20is%20that%20the%20C20%20can%20auto-detect%20carpet%20while%20it's%20mopping%20in%20which%20mopping%20pads%20stop%20spinning%20and%20raise%20up%20to%20avoid%20soaking%20the%20carpet.%20The%20bad%20news%20is%20that%20the%200.41-inch%20mop-lifting%20claim%20just%20isn't%20very%20much%20in%20practice%2C%20and%20I%20still%20had%20to%20manually%20clean%20a%20few%20spots%20of%20mustard%20after%20a%20cleaning%20pass%20because%20the%20pads%20couldn't%20lift%20high%20enough.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20its%20credit%2C%20however%2C%20the%20base%20station's%20mop%20pad%20washing%20feature%20did%20largely%20take%20care%20of%20the%20mess%2C%20and%20the%20robot%20didn't%20smear%20the%20condiment%20all%20over%20its%20undercarriage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254eed460-d930-4912-af60-fc23df4689be%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20features%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmart%20features%20and%20navigation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22screenshots%20from%20eufy%20robot%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a64b19a17a8c5b4053335a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Eufy%20app%20is%20your%20hub%20for%20customizing%20your%20settings%20and%20monitoring%20cleaning%20progress%20and%20accessory%20lifespan.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Eufy%20mobile%20app%20is%20polished%20and%20easy%20to%20navigate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20part%20I%20like%20about%20the%20app%2C%20as%20a%20nerd%2C%20is%20all%20the%20extended%20settings.%20You%20can%20tweak%20the%20map%2C%20adjust%20suction%20and%20water%20output%2C%20carpet%20cleaning%2C%20base%20station%20settings%2C%20robot%20settings%2C%20voice%20settings%2C%20and%20drive%20the%20robot%20manually.%20The%20app%20can%20also%20handle%20multiple%20cleaning%20schedules%20for%20different%20needs%2C%20such%20as%20vacuuming%20one%20room%20three%20days%20a%20week%20and%20a%20different%20room%20only%20once%20a%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20you%20see%20it%20as%20an%20upsell%2C%20the%20app%20tracks%20how%20much%20wear%20all%20of%20the%20sensors%2C%20brushes%2C%20and%20filters%20have%20endured%2C%20and%20when%20it's%20time%20to%20clean%20or%20replace%20them.%20Tapping%20on%20one%20of%20the%20items%20will%20show%20a%20picture%20of%20where%20the%20piece%20is%20located%2C%20how%20to%20handle%20it%2C%20and%20a%20purchase%20link%20if%20you%20need%20a%20replacement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20nice%20feature%2C%20not%20available%20for%20all%20robot%20cleaners%2C%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20share%20the%20device%20with%20someone%20else.%20They'll%20need%20to%20download%20the%20Eufy%20app%2C%20and%20then%2C%20it'll%20appear%20in%20their%20app%20for%20them%20to%20control%20and%20use%20just%20like%20it%20was%20theirs.%20Not%20only%20is%20it%20neat%2C%20but%20it%20worked%20exactly%20like%20I%20hoped%20it%20would.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20area%20where%20the%20C20%20is%20less%20smart%20is%20its%20navigation%E2%80%94specifically%20object%20avoidance.%20It%20forgoes%20LiDAR%20mounted%20on%20the%20top%2C%20in%20favor%20of%20it%20being%20positioned%20in%20the%20front.%20This%20keeps%20the%20unit%20thinner%20than%20others%2C%20but%20lacks%20cameras%20that%20can%20identify%20objects.%20Even%20on%20Eufy's%20website%2C%20tucked%20away%20when%20comparing%20models%2C%20it%20lists%20that%20this%20device%20isn't%20up%20to%20the%20task%20of%20avoiding%20pet%20waste%2C%20cords%2C%20and%20small%20toys.%20I%20saw%20most%20of%20those%20things%20in%20action%2C%20firsthand.%20Once%20it%20pulled%20a%20hanging%20plant%2C%20whose%20leaves%20were%20dangling%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20off%20a%20shelf.%20It%20also%20traveled%20over%20cords%20when%20they%20were%20left%20around.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20things%20may%20sound%20egregious%2C%20and%20they%20can%20be.%20I%20lost%20a%20beloved%20plant%20in%20the%20action!%20But%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20the%20C20%20navigated%20my%20floors%20just%20fine.%20Likely%2C%20the%20bigger%20concern%20for%20most%20people%20will%20be%20the%20unit's%20aggressiveness%20around%20certain%20types%20of%20furniture.%20I%20noticed%20it%20bumping%20into%20my%20dining%20chairs'%20thin%20legs%20harder%20than%20other%20robots%20%E2%80%94%20though%20not%20enough%20to%20damage%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%20baseboards%2C%20couches%2C%20and%20reclining%20chairs%2C%20it%20had%20no%20problem%20and%20slowed%20its%20approach.%20For%20the%20few%20places%20I%20do%20keep%20all%20robots%20away%20from%2C%20I%20added%20a%20no-go%20zone%20in%20the%20app.%20People%20with%20young%20kids%2C%20who%20constantly%20have%20random%20objects%20strewn%20across%20their%20floors%2C%20may%20want%20to%20avoid%20this%20model%20in%20favor%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110300303k2-20%26h%3D9f5ccc1a9993c6ed00decd898a980a8d63259675230361099e7cdd0a311174f6%26postID%3D68a63e0aacbb9be0ea793463%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Feufy-omni-c20-robot-vacuum-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0CPFBBHP4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOmni%20X10%20Pro%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20has%20bett