ich%20has%20been%20hailed%20as%20%26quot%3Berasing%26quot%3B%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20by%20an%20Israeli%20minister.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fuk-condemns-israels-approval-of-plans-for-new-west-bank-settlement-to-erase-idea-of-palestinian-state-13415376%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Flood-Hit%20Assam%20to%20Drought-Hit%20Maharashtra%3A%20The%2070%20Groups%20Protecting%20India%20from%20Climate%20Threats%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20tribal%20villages%20of%20rural%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20monsoon%20once%20meant%20baskets%20of%20freshly%20harvested%20millets%20in%20every%20home.%20These%20hardy%2C%20nutrient-rich%20grains%20sustained%20families%20for%20generations%2C%20keeping%20them%20fed%20and%20healthy.%20But%20today%2C%20shifting%20rainfall%20patterns%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20native%20seeds%20are%20threatening%20not%20just%20the%20harvest%2C%20but%20a%20way%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Pragati%20Abhiyan%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Nasik-based%20nonprofit%2C%20is%20working%20to%20bring%20these%20grains%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20nutrition%20they%20carry%20%E2%80%94%20back%20into%20local%20diets.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20solution%20or%20resilience-building%20effort%20must%20be%20tailored%20to%20meet%20the%20specific%20needs%20of%20these%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pranay%20Karuna%2C%20Associate%20Director%20at%20Dasra%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20philanthropic%20foundation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20means%20protecting%20indigenous%20knowledge%2C%20native%20seeds%2C%20and%20natural%20resources.%20From%20planning%20to%20execution%2C%20the%20work%20must%20consider%20all%20the%20different%20challenges%20these%20communities%20face.%20By%20focusing%20on%20farming%20and%20building%20local%20resilience%2C%20Pragati%20Abhiyan%20connects%20the%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%20with%20social%20inequalities%20and%20shows%20why%20solutions%20must%20be%20tailored%20to%20local%20needs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dasra%2C%20this%20approach%20is%20not%20new.%20Over%20the%20past%2025%20years%2C%20the%20foundation%20%E2%80%94%20co-founded%20by%20Neera%20Nundy%20and%20Deval%20Sanghavi%20%E2%80%94%20has%20directed%20more%20than%20%24420%20million%20toward%20social%20causes%2C%20supported%20over%201%2C400%20nonprofits%2C%20and%20positively%20impacted%20approximately%20200%20million%20lives.%20One%20of%20its%20most%20effective%20strategies%20has%20been%20to%20build%20alliances%20with%20like-minded%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%2010to19%20Alliance%2C%20which%20empowers%20adolescents%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20girls%20%E2%80%94%20to%20make%20positive%20life%20choices%2C%20to%20%E2%80%98Youth%20Ke%20Bol%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20building%20a%20coalition%20of%20one%20million%20young%20people%20for%20better%20access%20to%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20services%2C%20to%20the%20National%20Faecal%20Sludge%20and%20Septage%20Management%20(NFSSM)%20Alliance%2C%20which%20works%20with%20governments%20and%20municipalities%20on%20liquid%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20collaboration%20has%20always%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20Dasra%E2%80%99s%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20rural%20Maharashtra%2C%20Pragati%20Abhiyan%20is%20reviving%20native%20millet%20farming%20to%20fight%20malnutrition%20and%20climate%20stress.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-489104%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20rural%20Maharashtra%2C%20Pragati%20Abhiyan%20is%20reviving%20native%20millet%20farming%20to%20fight%20malnutrition%20and%20climate%20stress.%20(Representational%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fyoung-indian-farmer-standing-green-millet-2263537057%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20Dasra%2C%20every%20initiative%20has%20been%20rooted%20in%20collaborative%20action%20with%20communities%20at%20the%20centre.%20Through%20conversations%20with%20diverse%20organisations%2C%20we%20realised%20there%20was%20a%20significant%20gap%20in%20work%20around%20climate.%20This%20pushed%20us%20to%20explore%20it%20from%20an%20intersectional%20lens%2C%20focusing%20on%20strengthening%20community%20resilience.%20The%20aim%20was%20to%20shape%20an%20India%20view%2C%20create%20a%20common%20vocabulary%2C%20and%20enable%20multi-stakeholder%20engagement%20on%20climate%20action%20for%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pranay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20explore%20this%2C%20Dasra%20spoke%20with%20almost%20100%20organisations%20in%20its%20network%20that%20were%20working%20in%20climate-adjacent%20areas%2C%20seeking%20to%20understand%20what%20a%20dedicated%20climate%20alliance%20could%20look%20like.%20They%20already%20knew%20how%20to%20build%20alliances%2C%20but%20they%20wanted%20to%20hear%20directly%20from%20partners%20about%20priorities%20within%20the%20climate%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20emerged%20from%20these%20conversations%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98ClimateRISE%20Alliance%20(CRA)%E2%80%99%2C%20launched%20in%20early%202023.%20Bringing%20together%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20think%20tanks%2C%20intermediary%20groups%2C%20and%20funders%2C%20the%20CRA%20was%20established%20with%20support%20from%20Rainmatter%20Foundation%2C%20Oak%20Foundation%2C%20and%20MacArthur%20Foundation.%20Its%20aim%20is%20to%20shape%20%E2%80%9Can%20India%20view%E2%80%9D%20on%20intersectional%20climate%20action%2C%20create%20a%20common%20vocabulary%2C%20and%20enable%20multi-stakeholder%20engagement%20for%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities.%20Today%2C%20about%2070%20organisations%20are%20part%20of%20the%20CRA%2C%20with%20Dasra%20serving%20as%20its%20secretariat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-11_11zon-1-1755610423.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20in%20rural%20communities%20discuss%20local%20climate%20challenges%2C%20a%20key%20step%20in%20building%20resilience%20through%20the%20ClimateRISE%20Alliance.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-11_11zon-1-1755610423.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-11_11zon-1-1755610423-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-11_11zon-1-1755610423-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-11_11zon-1-1755610423-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-11_11zon-1-1755610423-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-489116%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOver%2025%20years%2C%20Dasra%20has%20channelled%20%24330M%20into%20social%20causes%2C%20building%20alliances%20like%20ClimateRISE%20for%20larger%20impact.%20(Representational%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fvillageneemtone-districtsehore-mp-india-december-20th-2417544213%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20solo%20efforts%20to%20a%20common%20table%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20organisations%20to%20join%20the%20CRA%20was%20%E2%80%98Janaagraha%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20nonprofit%20that%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20two%20decades%20working%20to%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20in%20Indian%20cities%20by%20collaborating%20with%20residents%2C%20governments%2C%20and%20urban%20local%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20organisation%20has%20been%20part%20of%20the%20CRA%20since%20its%20inception%20because%20we%20firmly%20believe%20that%20transforming%20our%20cities%20and%20addressing%20climate%20issues%20cannot%20be%20done%20in%20isolation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prarthana%20Ramesh%2C%20Associate%20Director%20at%20Janaagraha.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20CRA%20offers%20us%20an%20opportunity%20to%20collaborate%20with%20like-minded%20partners.%20It%20brings%20together%20diverse%20stakeholders%2C%20from%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20donors%20to%20innovative%20startups%2C%20to%20collectively%20address%20the%20climate%20crisis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Janaagraha%E2%80%99s%20key%20focus%20areas%20is%20bringing%20climate%20action%20to%20the%20local%20level%20in%20cities%20and%20towns.%20This%20means%20finding%20ways%20to%20make%20it%20part%20of%20everyday%20governance%20and%20tackling%20ongoing%20issues%20like%20flooding%2C%20heat%2C%20and%20poor%20air%20quality.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20help%20cities%20take%20charge%20and%20respond%20better%20to%20climate%20challenges%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prarthana%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20central%20to%20our%20work%20with%20the%20CRA%20%E2%80%94%20giving%20urban%20areas%20the%20tools%20and%20strategies%20they%20need%20to%20act%20effectively.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20early%20member%20was%20%E2%80%98Saahas%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20nonprofit%20specialising%20in%20solid%20waste%20management.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Saahas%20was%20working%20with%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20municipal%20bodies%20in%20northern%20Karnataka%20to%20strengthen%20local%20waste%20systems.%20While%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20Rainmatter%20Foundation%20for%20project%20assistance%2C%20they%20learnt%20about%20the%20CRA%E2%80%99s%20formation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-12_11zon-1755612395.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20Assam%2C%20CRA%20partners%20like%20Janaagraha%20are%20helping%20cities%20tackle%20flooding%2C%20heat%2C%20and%20poor%20air%20quality%20through%20local%20action.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-12_11zon-1755612395.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-12_11zon-1755612395-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-12_11zon-1755612395-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-12_11zon-1755612395-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-12_11zon-1755612395-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-489130%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20Assam%2C%20CRA%20partners%20like%20Janaagraha%20are%20helping%20cities%20tackle%20flooding%2C%20heat%2C%20and%20poor%20air%20quality%20through%20local%20action.%20(Representational%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fimpact-climate-change-heavy-rain-waterlogging-2182037783%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchana%20Tripathi%2C%20CEO%20of%20Saahas%2C%20remembers%20the%20turning%20point.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20approached%20Rainmatter%20Foundation%20and%20requested%20their%20support%2C%20we%20learnt%20about%20an%20alliance%20that%20was%20being%20put%20together%20with%20Dasra%20anchoring%20it.%20Despite%20working%20for%20years%20in%20the%20solid%20waste%20management%20sector%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20the%20climate%20space%20is%20much%20broader%20and%20that%20we%20need%20to%20collaborate%20with%20other%20organisations%20working%20on%20different%20climate-related%20issues%20such%20as%20air%20pollution%2C%20liquid%20waste%20management%2C%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20and%20similar%20subjects.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Archana%2C%20joining%20the%20CRA%20was%20about%20more%20than%20just%20networking.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20saw%20this%20alliance%20as%20a%20real%20opportunity%20to%20learn%20about%20what%20others%20in%20this%20space%20are%20doing%20and%20to%20help%20build%20a%20coherent%20narrative%20around%20climate.%20While%20you%20have%20the%20Disability%20Network%20Alliance%20(DNA)%20for%20organisations%20working%20on%20disabilities%2C%20there%20was%20no%20dedicated%20platform%20or%20alliance%20working%20on%20climate%20issues.%20Joining%20the%20CRA%20was%20a%20step%20towards%20filling%20that%20gap.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20alliance%20works%20on%20the%20ground%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CRA%E2%80%99s%20strength%20lies%20in%20its%20ability%20to%20bring%20different%20kinds%20of%20expertise%20to%20one%20table.%20Its%20work%20is%20organised%20into%20multiple%20streams%20%E2%80%94%20strategy%20development%2C%20capacity%20building%2C%20knowledge%20sharing%2C%20and%20collaborative%20advocacy.%20Within%20these%2C%20focus%20groups%20address%20specific%20themes%20such%20as%20gender%2C%20agroecology%20(sustainable%20farming%20that%20works%20with%20local%20ecosystems)%2C%20rural%20development%2C%20livelihoods%2C%20conservation%2C%20and%20restoration.%20Many%20of%20these%20areas%20overlap%2C%20making%20the%20alliance%20itself%20a%20climate-focused%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20approach%20is%20collaborative%2C%20not%20about%20one%20organisation%20taking%20a%20grant%20to%20run%20a%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Pranay.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20bring%20together%20stakeholders%20around%20a%20specific%20issue%20or%20idea%2C%20involving%20those%20who%20already%20have%20relevant%20expertise%2C%20ongoing%20projects%2C%20research%2C%20or%20resources.%20This%20pooling%20of%20knowledge%20and%20capacity%20allows%20us%20to%20address%20complex%20climate%20challenges%20in%20a%20coordinated%20and%20integrated%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20clear%20example%20of%20this%20approach%20is%20%E2%80%98Doh%20Shaher%2C%20Ek%20Rupayan%E2%80%99%20(DSER%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Ten%20Cities%2C%20One%20Vision%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20a%20convergence%20programme%20led%20by%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Department%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Affairs%20(DoHUA)%20to%20promote%20sustainable%20urbanisation%20in%2010%20large%20cities%20and%20towns.%20The%20programme%20covers%20critical%20climate-related%20components%20such%20as%20solid%20waste%20management%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20sanitation%2C%20blue-green%20infrastructure%2C%20urban%20planning%2C%20and%20more%20%E2%80%94%20bringing%20them%20together%20instead%20of%20working%20in%20silos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-13_11zon-1755612578.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bengaluru-based%20Saahas%20strengthens%20waste%20systems%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Assam%2C%20linking%20waste%20management%20with%20climate%20action.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-13_11zon-1755612578.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-13_11zon-1755612578-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-13_11zon-1755612578-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-13_11zon-1755612578-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-13_11zon-1755612578-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-489132%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBengaluru-based%20Saahas%20strengthens%20waste%20systems%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Assam%2C%20linking%20waste%20management%20with%20climate%20action.%20(Representational%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fnew-delhi-indiadec-15-2021-pwd-2106411422%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanaagraha%2C%20as%20an%20anchor%20partner%2C%20has%20been%20conducting%20field%20visits%20in%20Assam%20to%20understand%20the%20geography%20and%20identify%20needs.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20the%20partner%20organisations%20involved%20include%20Saahas%2C%20Consortium%20for%20DEWATS%20Dissemination%20(CDD)%20Society%20(decentralised%20wastewater%20treatment)%2C%20Centre%20for%20Water%20and%20Sanitation%20(CWAS)%2C%20Kushaagra%20Innovations%20Foundation%20(waste%20management%20solutions)%2C%20Hasiru%20Dala%20(waste%20management)%2C%20and%20Institute%20for%20Transportation%20and%20Development%20Policy%20(ITDP)%20India%20(public%20transport)%2C%20alongside%20local%20groups%20like%20Purvca%20Foundation%20(urban%20mobility)%20and%20The%20Midway%20Journey%20(decentralised%20waste%20management)%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prarthana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20CRA%2C%20working%20with%20local%20organisations%20like%20Purvca%20is%20essential.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20works%20in%20Purvanchal%20may%20not%20be%20suitable%20for%20urban%20Assam%20or%20coastal%20Karnataka%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pranay%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20region%20needs%20solutions%20designed%20for%20its%20own%20conditions%20and%20challenges.%20We%20believe%20climate%20action%20should%20be%20owned%20jointly%20by%20local%20communities%20and%20the%20government%2C%20with%20local%20bodies%2C%20district%20administrations%2C%20and%20grassroots%20organisations%20working%20together.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrarthana%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20role%20as%20Janaagraha%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20anchor%20partners%2C%20is%20to%20onboard%20and%20facilitate%20partners%20across%20these%20components%2C%20but%20not%20in%20a%20siloed%20way.%20The%20CRA%20connects%20us%20with%20the%20best%20minds%20across%20sanitation%2C%20solid%20waste%20management%2C%20blue-green%20infrastructure%2C%20urban%20planning%2C%20mobility%2C%20and%20urban%20transport.%20We%20bring%20these%20experts%20together%20to%20think%20creatively%20and%20reimagine%20what%20urbanisation%20can%20look%20like%20for%20these%20cities%20and%20towns.%20We%20aim%20to%20help%20the%20government%20build%20internal%20capacity%20to%20change%20the%20current%20narrative%2C%20as%20well%20as%20introduce%20elements%20of%20innovation%20into%20their%20planning%20and%20thinking%20processes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20part%20of%20the%20DSER%20project%20is%20developing%20%E2%80%98City%20Action%20Plans%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20short-term%2C%20bottom-up%20vision%20documents%20created%20with%20citizen%20input%2C%20reflecting%20local%20contexts%20and%20aspirations%20for%20the%20next%2025%20years.%20These%20plans%20list%20practical%20projects%20and%20initiatives%2C%20aiming%20to%20be%20living%20documents%20that%20evolve%20with%20the%20cities%20instead%20of%20gathering%20dust%20like%20many%20long-term%20master%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-14_11zon-1755612744.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Climate%20resilience%20projects%20also%20build%20women%E2%80%99s%20skills%20and%20livelihoods%2C%20making%20communities%20stronger%20against%20future%20shocks.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-14_11zon-1755612744.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-14_11zon-1755612744-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-14_11zon-1755612744-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-14_11zon-1755612744-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-14_11zon-1755612744-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-489134%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20CRA%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Doh%20Shaher%2C%20Ek%20Rupayan%E2%80%99%20programme%20in%20Assam%20unites%20citizens%2C%20governments%2C%20and%20NGOs%20to%20plan%20climate-ready%20cities.%20(Repres